149cdb45-9287-4218-b85e-eb7e216f208e.title: <player>
149cdb45-9287-4218-b85e-eb7e216f208e.text: You seem to like playing with danger, there.

361eec6a-0cc3-40b3-aa8c-3a8f66521103.title: 'No fingers'
361eec6a-0cc3-40b3-aa8c-3a8f66521103.text: They don't call me 'No-fingers' for nothing!

4f363177-aee0-4880-ad4b-69ac43c9c24d.title: <player>
4f363177-aee0-4880-ad4b-69ac43c9c24d.text:
Well, correct me if I'm wrong, but you seem to have all
your fingers.

17095084-004d-48f9-9ac7-90889d64ad22.title: 'No fingers'
17095084-004d-48f9-9ac7-90889d64ad22.text:
It may seem that way mate, but I think you'll find I
don't have any.

3912c17e-153e-46b1-9216-cc25d4c2b927.title: 'No fingers'
3912c17e-153e-46b1-9216-cc25d4c2b927.text: These not be fingers. These 'ere be wooden fingers.

8fc91461-51e3-4783-aa3b-00c176fb3e76.title: <player>
8fc91461-51e3-4783-aa3b-00c176fb3e76.text: That's not possible, how could you move them?

67cb894b-06ca-46de-ae0e-14414ab9017b.title: <player>
67cb894b-06ca-46de-ae0e-14414ab9017b.text: Yes, well I think I'd better be going now.

4f0878d3-94d9-475b-8a03-98e9cfcf5474.title: <player>
4f0878d3-94d9-475b-8a03-98e9cfcf5474.text:
Hello. I was just wondering... I don't suppose you have
any spare clothing you could lend me?

71ea4527-3339-44eb-ac47-76e9d1ee22c3.title: 'No fingers'
71ea4527-3339-44eb-ac47-76e9d1ee22c3.text: But there's no way I'm giving any to you.

46e98dce-48ac-4f91-8e51-f08d8bd29551.title: <player>
46e98dce-48ac-4f91-8e51-f08d8bd29551.text: Oh, but why? I could pay you!

5a168ab0-2ae7-4c98-83e8-11aec970bccc.title: 'No fingers'
5a168ab0-2ae7-4c98-83e8-11aec970bccc.text:
Nope. Only real builders can wear builders' boots, and
you're not even close.

dcb01868-ce68-4fdc-a8cf-3ea3295e6744.title: 'No fingers'
dcb01868-ce68-4fdc-a8cf-3ea3295e6744.text: Well, I am. Have you seen-

aaf2cf2a-9812-4e5c-9ef6-6594a04a5654.title: <player>
aaf2cf2a-9812-4e5c-9ef6-6594a04a5654.text: Oh no! I left the oven on! Got to go, sorry!

87d193bd-22c8-405a-827d-f6917c8013e5.title: 'No fingers'
87d193bd-22c8-405a-827d-f6917c8013e5.text:
Don't suppose you've seen any boots around here? Size
nine, steel toed, brown leather...

be5232db-69f0-4565-bbc2-a1d8b1179509.title: <player>
be5232db-69f0-4565-bbc2-a1d8b1179509.text:
Nope, not at all. I'd best be going. Have a nice day.
Bye!
